spirit of patriotism and work hard to contribute to a stable
transition and a smooth handover of power in Macao in 1999," he
added.
</P>
<P>
"The film will inspire people's patriotism," said Kou. "It
will reveal the truth that only when a national reunification and
prosperity is reached can China stand firm among nations in the
world."  
