<HEADLINE> People's Congress of Chongqing Municipality Opens First Meeting </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHONGQING, June 8 (Xinhua) -- The first session of the first
Municipal People's Congress of Chongqing, China's youngest and
