<P>
The meeting will also review a number of work reports, such as
the work report of the municipal government and the work report on
migration.
</P>
<P>
Chongqing's plan for economic and social development during the
Ninth Five-Year Plan period (1996-2000) and its long-range
objectives to the year 2010 will be decided during the meeting.
</P>
<P>
The meeting is expected to greatly promote reform, opening-up
and economic and social development in Chongqing, which was
promoted to the provincial status by the Fifth Session of the
Eighth National People's Congress on March 14 this year.
</P>
<P>
China's three other municipalities are Beijing, Tianjin and
Shanghai. 
</P>
</TEXT>
