<P>
LAGOS, June 7 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria became the first country to
qualify for the '98 France World Cup as its Super Eagles beat the
Harambee Stars of Kenya 3-0 in an African Group A qualifier Sunday
in the National Stadium in Lagos.
</P>
