substitute Wilson Oruma stroke for the third goal at the 84th
minute.
</P>
<P>
Nigeria now leads Group A with 13 points from four wins and one
draw. With only one more match against Guinea to go, the team has
actually got the ticket to '98 France World Cup, the first among
the 172 teams worldwide.
</P>
<P>
In the same group, Kenya follows Nigeria with seven points.
Guinea holds the third position with six points. Burkina Faso has
lost all the games. 
